data.description: **MAJOR PRICE IMPROVEMENT** Enjoy one level living in this updated & spacious ranch home in highly desirable Abercrombie Woods! Loads of curb appeal outside, well manicured lawn, warm stone facade & welcoming covered front porch. Inside features gorgeous hickory floors, tall ceilings & dramatic stone fireplace. Galley style kitchen w/SS appliances & walk in pantry flows right into the dining room. Step out the back door onto the brand new deck to enjoy the outdoors. Tuff Shed stays. Back inside, you'll find the main bedroom suite, two nice sized bedrooms & recently renovated full hall bath. Main bedroom features a huge ensuite bathroom w/ jetted tub, separate shower, toilet room & walk in closet. Attached to the main bedroom is a separate flexible space, use as an office or could also be a nursery or extra closet space. Heated garage/man cave w/lots of storage! Updates: 2019 HWH 2020 Roof/Gutters & Crawlspace Encapsulation 2022 Tuff Shed 2023 Deck.
